CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: Reneva Biosciences Ltd. is a newly incorporated company established by Giant Biogene Holding Co., Ltd. as part of a strategic spin-off. It was formed to take over certain early-stage research and development assets and businesses that are not directly related to Giant Biogene's core collagen-based operations.
